quran[11{c,v,t}:
19,1,Kaaaf-Haa-Yaa-'Ayyyn-Saaad
19,2,Zikru rahmati Rabbika 'abdahoo Zakariyya
19,3,Iz naadaa Rabbahoo nidaaa'an khafiyyaa
19,4,Qaala Rabbi innee wahanal'azmu minnee washta'alar raasu shaibanw wa lam akum bidu'aaa'ika Rabbi shaqiyyaa
19,5,Wa innee khiftul mawaa liya minw waraaa'ee wa kaana tim ra atee 'aairan fahab lee mil ladunka waliyyaa
19,6,"Yarisunee wa yarisu min aali Ya'qoob, waj'alhu Rabbi radiyya"
19,7,Yaa Zakariyyaaa innaa nubashshiruka bighulaami nismuhoo Yahyaa lam naj'al lahoo min qablu samiyyaa
19,8,Qaala Rabbi annaa yakoonu lee ghulaamunw wa kaanatim ra atee aaqiranw wa qad balaghtu minal kibari 'itiyyaa
19,9,Qaala kazaalika qaala Rabbuka huwa 'alaiya haiyinunw wa qad khalaqtuka min qablu wa lam taku shai'aa
19,10,Qaala Rabbij 'al leee Aayah; qaala Aayatuka allaa tukalliman naasa salaasa layaalin sawiyyaa
19,11,Fakharaja 'alaa qawmihee minal mihraabi fa-awhaaa ilaihim an sabbihoo bukratanw wa 'ashiyyaa
